  <li><strong>野菜</strong>を戻し、<strong>甜麵醬</strong>、<strong>鶏がらスープの素</strong>で味をつける</li>
  <li><strong>水溶き片栗粉</strong>を加え、とろみをつける</li>
</ol>]]></content><author><name>yuki_kamikita</name></author><category term="食事" /><category term="ひき肉" /><category term="なす" /><category term="豆板醤" /><category term="甜麵醬" /><category term="片栗粉" /><category term="生姜" /><category term="中華料理" /><category term="主菜" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">回鍋肉</title><link href="https://yuki-kamikita.github.io/kurashino/%E9%A3%9F%E4%BA%8B/%E5%9B%9E%E9%8D%8B%E8%82%89.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="回鍋肉" /><published>2025-02-14T04:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2025-02-14T04:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://yuki-kamikita.github.io/kurashino/%E9%A3%9F%E4%BA%8B/%E5%9B%9E%E9%8D%8B%E8%82%89</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://yuki-kamikita.github.io/kurashino/%E9%A3%9F%E4%BA%8B/%E5%9B%9E%E9%8D%8B%E8%82%89.html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="/kurashino/assets/images/hoikoro.jpg" alt="回鍋肉" /></p>

